                              <desc>The name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3430DawitII">Dāwit III</persName> is mentioned.</desc>
                            </item>
                            <item xml:id="e2">
                              <desc>The manuscript was ordered by
                                <persName role="donor" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13506WaldaD">Walda Dam</persName> and by his female relative
                              <persName role="donor" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13507Maqdasawit">Maqdasāwit</persName> (<locus target="#2r #77r #162v"/>).
                            The names of the two later owners are <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13508WaldaM">Wada Māryām</persName>
                          and his wife <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13509EdaH">ʿƎḍa Ḥǝywat</persName>.</desc>
                            </item>
                          </list>

